summary: Should I just make video essays nagging about Moomin? I have too much to talk about. Old video I made about various film...
body:
Should I just make video essays nagging about Moomin? I have too much to talk about. Old video I made about various film adaptations once, something in English would probably reach out a bit further.
Primarily this is a subject no one talks in depth about, I feel we need someone to be that obnoxious dork. That could be me!

summary: Considering the new show messes up the canon by mixing in the newspaper strip stuff in the very first episode, I'll just take...
body:
Considering the new show messes up the canon by mixing in the newspaper strip stuff in the very first episode, I’ll just take the good with the bad and wish for a martian episode right away.

If you want to fundamentally misunderstand the source material, at least give me 3D Marsmom in exchange.
